Company Overview of CA Indosuez Wealth (Europe) S.A.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
CA Indosuez Wealth (Europe) S.A. provides private banking products and services. It offers open-ended investment funds that include flexible funds, fixed income funds, and equity funds; and life insurance products. The company also provides financial and estate planning services; discretionary management for security, prudent, balanced, growth, and dynamic investment profiles; trust services; wealth management for family offices; and asset and financial engineering and agency services. In addition, it offers Internet banking solutions. CA Indosuez Wealth (Europe) S.A. was formerly known as Credit Agricole Luxembourg SA and changed its name to CA Indosuez Wealth (Europe) S.A. in January 2016....
CA Indosuez Wealth (Europe) S.A. provides private banking products and services. It offers open-ended investment funds that include flexible funds, fixed income funds, and equity funds; and life insurance products. The company also provides financial and estate planning services; discretionary management for security, prudent, balanced, growth, and dynamic investment profiles; trust services; wealth management for family offices; and asset and financial engineering and agency services. In addition, it offers Internet banking solutions. CA Indosuez Wealth (Europe) S.A. was formerly known as Credit Agricole Luxembourg SA and changed its name to CA Indosuez Wealth (Europe) S.A. in January 2016. The company was founded in 1920 and is based in Luxembourg. It has additional offices in Madrid, Bilbao, Valencia, and San Sebastian, Spain. CA Indosuez Wealth (Europe) S.A. operates as a subsidiary of Credit Agricole S.A.
