CA Indosuez Wealth Management is 
a division of Crédit Agricole Group (France). 
CA Indosuez Wealth Management provides a broad range of products and services in 
private banking, international asset management and financial advising. In 2015 total assets of CA Indosuez Wealth (Europe)  were 5 406,00 mln EUR.  In 2015 the bank's annual profit was 45,00 mln EUR.  CA Indosuez Wealth (Europe) participates in deposit guarantee scheme of Luxembourg. 
This scheme covers accounts up to 100 000 EUR per bank per depositor.  CA Indosuez Wealth (Europe) is headquartered in LUXEMBOURG.




Address39, allée Scheffer, 2520, LUXEMBOURG, LuxembourgP.O. Box1104 

Member of Group Crédit Agricole (France)  
 


