Company Overview of Credit Agricole CIB Financial Products (Guernsey) Limited



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Credit Agricole CIB Financial Products (Guernsey) Limited issues notes or warrants with pay offs linked to underlying equity, index, and funds. Its notes and warrants are issued on Luxembourg stock exchange. The company also provides derivatives, such as swaps and options. Credit Agricole CIB Financial Products (Guernsey) Limited is based in St Peter Port, the Channel Islands. Credit Agricole CIB Financial Products (Guernsey) Limited is a subsidiary of Credit Agricole CIB.


Sarnia HouseLe TruchotSt Peter Port,  GYI 4NAChannel Islands










